trans-unit.source: QBoxLayout also includes two margin widths:
QBoxLayout takes the space it gets (from its parent layout or from the parentWidget()), divides it up into a row of boxes, and makes each managed widget fill one box.
trans-unit.target: QBoxLayout占用它获得的空间（从其父布局或从parentWidget（）），将其划分为一行框，并使每个托管窗口小部件填充一个框。

trans-unit.target: addLayout（）将包含另一个QLayout的框添加到该行，并设置该布局的拉伸因子。

trans-unit.source: addSpacing() to create an empty box; this is one of the functions you use to create nice and spacious dialogs. See below for ways to set margins.
trans-unit.target: addSpacing（）创建一个空盒子；这是用于创建美观大方对话框的功能之一。有关设置边距的方法，请参见下文。

trans-unit.source: addStretch() to create an empty, stretchable box.
addWidget() to add a widget to the QBoxLayout and set the widget's stretch factor. (The stretch factor is along the row of boxes.)

trans-unit.source: addWidget() to add a widget to the QBoxLayout and set the widget's stretch factor. (The stretch factor is along the row of boxes.)

trans-unit.target: setSpacing（）设置相邻框之间的宽度。（您可以使用addSpacing（）在特定位置获得更多空间。）

trans-unit.source: QBuffer emits readyRead() when new data has arrived in the buffer. By connecting to this signal, you can use QBuffer to store temporary data before processing it. QBuffer also emits bytesWritten() every time new data has been written to the buffer.

trans-unit.source: QButtonGroup provides an abstract container into which button widgets can be placed. It does not provide a visual representation of this container (see QGroupBox for a container widget), but instead manages the states of each of the buttons in the group.
trans-unit.target: QButtonGroup提供了一个抽象的容器，可以在其中放置按钮小部件。它不提供此容器的直观表示（有关容器小部件，请参见QGroupBox），而是管理组中每个按钮的状态。

trans-unit.source: QByteArray and QList<T> use more or less the same algorithm as QString.
trans-unit.target: QByteArray和QList <T>使用与QString大致相同的算法。

trans-unit.source: QByteArray can be used to store both raw bytes (including '\0's) and traditional 8-bit '\0'-terminated strings. Using QByteArray is much more convenient than using const char *. Behind the scenes, it always ensures that the data is followed by a '\0' terminator, and uses implicit sharing (copy-on-write) to reduce memory usage and avoid needless copying of data.
trans-unit.target: QByteArray可用于存储原始字节（包括'\ 0'）和传统的8位'\ 0'终止的字符串。使用QByteArray比使用 const char * 更方便。在幕后，它始终确保数据后跟一个'\ 0'终结符，并使用隐式共享（写时复制）来减少内存使用并避免不必要的数据复制。

trans-unit.source: QByteArray makes a deep copy of the const char * data, so you can modify it later without experiencing side effects. (If for performance reasons you don't want to take a deep copy of the character data, use QByteArray::fromRawData() instead.)
trans-unit.target: QByteArray对 const char * 数据进行了深层复制，因此您以后可以修改它而不会出现副作用。（如果出于性能原因，您不想复制字符数据的深层副本，请改用QByteArray :: fromRawData（）。）

trans-unit.source: QByteArray makes a deep copy of the string data.
trans-unit.target: QByteArray对字符串数据进行深层复制。

trans-unit.source: QByteArray provides the following basic functions for modifying the byte data: append(), prepend(), insert(), replace(), and remove(). For example:

trans-unit.source: QByteArrays can be compared using overloaded operators such as operator<(), operator<=(), operator==(), operator>=(), and so on. The comparison is based exclusively on the numeric values of the characters and is very fast, but is not what a human would expect. QString::localeAwareCompare() is a better choice for sorting user-interface strings.
trans-unit.target: 可以使用重载运算符（例如operator <（），operator <=（），operator ==（），operator> =（）等）比较QByteArray。这种比较仅基于字符的数值，并且非常快，但不是人们期望的。QString :: localeAwareCompare（）是对用户界面字符串进行排序的更好选择。

trans-unit.source: at() can be faster than operator[](), because it never causes a deep copy to occur.
trans-unit.target: at（）可以比operator []（）更快，因为它永远不会引起深层复制。

trans-unit.source: QByteArray::fromBase64() ignores the KeepTrailingEquals and OmitTrailingEquals options and will not flag errors in case they are missing or if there are too many of them.
trans-unit.target: QByteArray :: fromBase64（）会忽略KeepTrailingEquals和OmitTrailingEquals选项，并且在丢失或错误过多的情况下不会标记错误。

trans-unit.source: QByteArray::fromBase64Encoding() and QByteArray::fromBase64() ignore the KeepTrailingEquals and OmitTrailingEquals options. If the IgnoreBase64DecodingErrors option is specified, they will not flag errors in case trailing equal signs are missing or if there are too many of them. If instead the AbortOnBase64DecodingErrors is specified, then the input must either have no padding or have the correct amount of equal signs.
QByteArrayList is actually just a QList<QByteArray>. It is documented as a full class just for simplicity of documenting the member methods that exist only in QList<QByteArray>.
trans-unit.target: QByteArrayList实际上只是一个QList < QByteArray >。仅出于记录仅存在于QList < QByteArray >中的成员方法的简单起见，将其记录为完整类。

trans-unit.source: QByteArrayList provides both Java-style iterators and STL-style iterators. The Java-style const iterator is simply a type definition for QListIterator<QByteArray>.
trans-unit.target: QByteArrayList提供Java样式的迭代器和STL样式的迭代器。Java样式的const迭代器只是QListIterator < QByteArray > 的类型定义。

trans-unit.source: QByteArrayList provides both Java-style iterators and STL-style iterators. The Java-style non-const iterator is simply a type definition for QMutableListIterator<QByteArray>.
trans-unit.target: QByteArrayList提供Java样式的迭代器和STL样式的迭代器。Java风格的非常量迭代器只是QMutableListIterator < QByteArray > 的类型定义。

trans-unit.source: QCalendarWidget (2) provides a monthly calendar widget that can be used to select dates.
trans-unit.target: QCalendarWidget（2）提供每月的日历小部件，可用于选择日期。

trans-unit.source: QCamera also emits lockStatusChanged(QCamera::LockType, QCamera::LockStatus) on individual lock status changes and lockStatusChanged(QCamera::LockStatus) signal on composite status changes.

trans-unit.source: QCamera can be used with QCameraViewfinder for viewfinder display, QMediaRecorder for video recording and QCameraImageCapture for image taking.
trans-unit.target: QCamera可以与QCameraViewfinder一起用于取景器显示，QMediaRecorder可以用于视频记录，QCameraImageCapture可以用于图像拍摄。

trans-unit.target: QCamera保存所有捕获参数，例如曝光设置或图像处理参数，因此在调用capture（）之后对照相机参数的更改不会影响先前的捕获请求。

trans-unit.source: QCameraInfo lets you query for camera devices that are currently available on the system.
trans-unit.target: QCameraInfo使您可以查询系统上当前可用的相机设备。

trans-unit.source: QCanBus loads Qt CAN Bus plugins at runtime. The ownership of serial bus plugins is transferred to the loader.
trans-unit.target: QCanBus在运行时加载Qt CAN Bus插件。串行总线插件的所有权已转移到加载程序。

trans-unit.source: QCanBus provides an API to create a QCanBusDevice from a chosen plugin.
trans-unit.target: QCanBus提供了一个API，可从所选插件创建QCanBusDevice。

trans-unit.source: QCanBusDevice can use QCanBusFrame for read and write operations. It contains the frame identifier and the data payload. QCanBusFrame contains the timestamp of the moment it was read.
trans-unit.target: QCanBusDevice可以使用QCanBusFrame进行读写操作。它包含帧标识符和数据有效载荷。QCanBusFrame包含读取时刻的时间戳。

trans-unit.source: QCanBusDevice can use QCanBusFrame for read and write operations. It contains the frame identifier and the data payload. QCanBusFrame contains the timestamp of the moment it was read.
QCanBusDevice communicates with a CAN plugin providing users with a convenient API. The CAN plugin must be specified during the object creation.
trans-unit.target: QCanBusDevice与CAN插件通信，为用户提供了便捷的API。必须在对象创建期间指定CAN插件。

trans-unit.source: QCanBusDevice provides an API for direct access to the CAN device.
QCanBusDevice::ReceiveOwnKey must be set to true to receive echo frames.
trans-unit.target: QCanBusDevice :: ReceiveOwnKey必须设置为true才能接收回显帧。

trans-unit.source: QCanBusDevice::writeFrame() is responsible for sanity checks such as the validity of the QCanBusFrame and that the device is still connected. Provided that the checks passed, it writes the frame to the CAN bus. Upon success it emits the QCanBusDevice::framesWritten() signal; otherwise QCanBusDevice::setError() is called with an appropriate error message. This function may also be used to implement an asynchronous write operation. It is the plugin implementors responsibility to emit the appropriate signals at the appropriate time.
trans-unit.target: QCanBusDevice :: writeFrame（）负责完整性检查，例如QCanBusFrame的有效性以及设备是否仍处于连接状态。假设检查通过，则将帧写入CAN总线。成功后，它将发出QCanBusDevice :: framesWritten（）信号；否则，将使用适当的错误消息调用QCanBusDevice :: setError（）。此功能也可以用于实现异步写入操作。插件实施者有责任在适当的时间发出适当的信号。

trans-unit.source: QCanBusDeviceInfo provides information about available CAN devices.
QCanBusFrame defines a CAN frame that can be written and read from QCanBusDevice.
trans-unit.target: QCanBusFrame定义可以从QCanBusDevice写入和读取的CAN帧。

trans-unit.source: QCanBusFrame is a container class representing a single CAN frame. More...
trans-unit.target: QCanBusFrame是表示单个CAN帧的容器类。更多...

trans-unit.source: QCandlestickLegendMarker is related to QCandlestickSeries, so that one candlestick series results in one marker.
trans-unit.target: QCandlestickLegendMarker有关QCandlestickSeries在一个标记，使一个烛台一系列成果。

trans-unit.source: QCategory3DAxis provides an axis that can be given labels. The axis is divided into equal-sized categories based on the data window size defined by setting the axis range.
trans-unit.target: QCategory3DAxis提供了可以为其指定标签的轴。根据通过设置轴范围定义的数据窗口大小，将轴分为大小相等的类别。

trans-unit.source: QCborArray is very similar to QVariantList and QJsonArray and its API is almost identical to those two classes. It can also be converted to and from those two, though there may be loss of information in some conversions.
trans-unit.target: QCborArray与QVariantList和QJsonArray非常相似，其API与这两个类几乎相同。尽管在某些转换中可能会丢失信息，但也可以在这两个之间进行转换。

trans-unit.source: QCborArray::ConstIterator allows you to iterate over a QCborArray. If you want to modify the QCborArray as you iterate over it, use QCborArray::Iterator instead. It is generally good practice to use QCborArray::ConstIterator, even on a non-const QCborArray, when you don't need to change the QCborArray through the iterator. Const iterators are slightly faster and improves code readability.
trans-unit.target: QCborArray :: ConstIterator允许您遍历QCborArray。如果要在迭代过程中修改QCborArray，请改用QCborArray :: Iterator。它一般是用好的做法QCborArray :: ConstIterator，即使在非const QCborArray，当你不需要改变QCborArray通过迭代。常量迭代器的速度稍快一些，并提高了代码的可读性。

trans-unit.source: QCborArray::Iterator allows you to iterate over a QCborArray and to modify the array item associated with the iterator. If you want to iterate over a const QCborArray, use QCborArray::ConstIterator instead. It is generally a good practice to use QCborArray::ConstIterator on a non-const QCborArray as well, unless you need to change the QCborArray through the iterator. Const iterators are slightly faster and improve code readability.
trans-unit.target: QCborArray :: Iterator允许您遍历QCborArray并修改与迭代器关联的数组项。如果要遍历const QCborArray，请改用QCborArray :: ConstIterator。它一般是用一个很好的做法QCborArray :: ConstIterator在非const QCborArray，除非你需要更改QCborArray通过迭代。常量迭代器的速度稍快一些，并提高了代码的可读性。

trans-unit.source: QCborMap can also be converted to and from QVariantMap and QJsonObject. However, when performing the conversion, any non-string keys will be stringified using a one-way method that the conversion back to QCborMap will not undo.
trans-unit.target: QCborMap也可以与QVariantMap和QJsonObject相互转换。但是，在执行转换时，将使用单向方法对任何非字符串键进行字符串化，这样返回QCborMap的转换将不会撤消。

trans-unit.source: QCborMap is not sorted, because of that, searching for keys has linear complexity (O(n)). QCborMap actually keeps the elements in the order that they were inserted, which means that it is possible to make sorted QCborMaps by carefully inserting elements in sorted order. CBOR does not require sorting, but recommends it.
trans-unit.target: QCborMap未排序，因此，搜索键具有线性复杂度（O（n））。QCborMap实际上按插入顺序保留元素，这意味着可以通过按排序顺序仔细插入元素来进行排序的QCborMap。CBOR不需要排序，但建议进行排序。

trans-unit.source: QCborMap: an associative container of QCborValues

trans-unit.target: QCborMap :: iterator QCborMap :: erase（QCborMap :: iterator

trans-unit.source: QCborMap::ConstIterator allows you to iterate over a QCborMap. If you want to modify the QCborMap as you iterate over it, you must use QCborMap::Iterator instead. It is generally good practice to use QCborMap::ConstIterator, even on a non-const QCborMap, when you don't need to change the QCborMap through the iterator. Const iterators are slightly faster and improve code readability.
trans-unit.target: QCborMap :: ConstIterator允许您迭代QCborMap。如果要在迭代过程中修改QCborMap，则必须改用QCborMap :: Iterator。它一般是用好的做法QCborMap :: ConstIterator，即使在非const QCborMap，当你不需要改变你QCborMap通过迭代。常量迭代器的速度稍快一些，并提高了代码的可读性。

trans-unit.source: QCborMap::Iterator allows you to iterate over a QCborMap and to modify the value (but not the key) stored under a particular key. If you want to iterate over a const QCborMap, you should use QCborMap::ConstIterator. It is generally good practice to use QCborMap::ConstIterator on a non-const QCborMap as well, unless you need to change the QCborMap through the iterator. Const iterators are slightly faster, and improve code readability.
trans-unit.target: QCborMap :: Iterator允许您遍历QCborMap并修改存储在特定键下的值（而不是键）。如果要遍历const QCborMap，则应使用QCborMap :: ConstIterator。它一般是用好的做法QCborMap :: ConstIterator在非const QCborMap，除非你需要更改QCborMap通过迭代。常量迭代器的速度稍快一些，并提高了代码的可读性。

trans-unit.source: QCborStreamReader is capable of detecting corrupt input on its own. The library it uses has been extensively tested against invalid input of any kind and is quite able to report errors. If any is detected, QCborStreamReader will set lastError() to a value besides QCborError::NoError, indicating which situation was detected.
trans-unit.target: QCborStreamReader能够自行检测损坏的输入。它使用的库已经针对各种无效输入进行了广泛的测试，并且能够报告错误。如果检测到任何情况，QCborStreamReader会将lastError（）设置为QCborError :: NoError以外的值，指示检测到哪种情况。

trans-unit.source: QCborStreamReader provides a StAX-like API, similar to that of QXmlStreamReader. Using it requires a bit of knowledge of CBOR encoding. For a simpler API, see QCborValue and especially the decoding function QCborValue::fromCbor().
trans-unit.target: QCborStreamReader提供类似于StAX的API，类似于QXmlStreamReader。使用它需要一些CBOR编码知识。有关更简单的API，请参见QCborValue，尤其是解码函数QCborValue :: fromCbor（）。

trans-unit.source: QCborStreamReader::next() was called but there are no more elements in the current context.
trans-unit.target: 调用了QCborStreamReader :: next（），但当前上下文中没有其他元素。

trans-unit.source: QCborStreamWriter does not perform error checking to see if all required items were written to the stream prior to the object being destroyed. It is the programmer's responsibility to ensure that it was done.
trans-unit.target: QCborStreamWriter不会执行错误检查，以查看在销毁对象之前是否所有必需项都已写入流中。程序员有责任确保已完成。

trans-unit.source: QCborStreamWriter has no buffering, so every append() call will result in one or more calls to the device's write() method.
trans-unit.target: QCborStreamWriter没有缓冲，因此每个append（）调用都会导致对设备的write（）方法的一个或多个调用。

trans-unit.source: QCborStreamWriter provides a StAX-like API, similar to that of QXmlStreamWriter. It is rather low-level and requires a bit of knowledge of CBOR encoding. For a simpler API, see QCborValue and especially the encoding function QCborValue::toCbor().
trans-unit.target: QCborStreamWriter提供类似于StAX的API，类似于QXmlStreamWriter。它相当底层，需要一些CBOR编码知识。有关更简单的API，请参见QCborValue，尤其是编码函数QCborValue :: toCbor（）。

trans-unit.source: QCborStreamWriter supports all CBOR features required to create canonical and strict streams. It implements almost all of the features specified in RFC 7049.
trans-unit.target: QCborStreamWriter支持创建规范和严格流所需的所有CBOR功能。它实现了RFC 7049中指定的几乎所有功能。

trans-unit.source: QCborValue can also be of the undefined type, which represents a value of "undefined". In fact, that is what the QCborValue default constructor creates.
trans-unit.target: QCborValue也可以是未定义类型，表示“未定义”值。实际上，这就是QCborValue默认构造函数创建的。

trans-unit.source: QCborValue can contain a value of "null", which is not of any specific type. It resembles the C++ std::nullptr_t type, whose only possible value is nullptr. QCborValue has a constructor taking such a type and creates a null QCborValue.
trans-unit.target: QCborValue可以包含“ null”值，该值不是任何特定类型。它类似于C ++ std::nullptr_t 类型，其唯一可能的值为 nullptr 。QCborValue具有采用这种类型的构造函数，并创建一个空QCborValue。

trans-unit.source: QCborValue object into this one and frees the resources of this one.

trans-unit.target: QCborValue对象进入这一对象并释放这一资源。返回对此对象的引用。

trans-unit.source: QCborValue objects with undefined values are also different from invalid QCborValue objects. The API will not create invalid QCborValues, but they may exist as a result of a parsing error.
trans-unit.target: 带有未定义值的QCborValue对象也与无效QCborValue对象不同。该API不会创建无效的QCborValue，但由于解析错误，它们可能存在。

trans-unit.source: QCborValue supports all CBOR features required to create canonical and strict streams. It implements almost all of the features specified in RFC 7049.
trans-unit.target: QCborValue支持创建规范流和严格流所需的所有CBOR功能。它实现了RFC 7049中指定的几乎所有功能。

trans-unit.source: QCborValue will always convert half- and single-precision floating point values in the CBOR stream to double-precision. The toCbor() function can take a parameter indicating to recreate them.
trans-unit.target: QCborValue将始终将CBOR流中的半精度和单精度浮点值转换为双精度。所述toCbor（）函数可以取指示重新创建它们的参数。

trans-unit.source: fromCbor() is able to decode chunked strings, but will always merge the chunks together into a single QCborValue. For that reason, it always writes non-chunked strings when using toCbor() (which is required by the Canonical format anyway).
trans-unit.target: fromCbor（）能够解码分块字符串，但始终会将这些分块合并到一个QCborValue中。因此，在使用toCbor（）时，它总是写非块化字符串（无论如何，这是规范格式所必需的）。

trans-unit.source: fromCbor() is able to decode chunked strings, but will always merge the chunks together into a single QCborValue. For that reason, it always writes non-chunked strings when using toCbor() (which is required by the Canonical format anyway).
QCborValueRef has the exact same API as QCborValue, with one important difference: if you assign new values to it, this array will be updated with that new value.
trans-unit.target: QCborValueRef具有与QCborValue完全相同的API，但有一个重要区别：如果您为其分配新值，则将使用该新值更新该数组。

trans-unit.source: QCborValueRef has the exact same API as QCborValue, with one important difference: if you assign new values to it, this map will be updated with that new value.
trans-unit.target: QCborValueRef具有与QCborValue完全相同的API，但有一个重要区别：如果您为其分配新值，则此映射将使用该新值进行更新。

trans-unit.source: QCborValueRef is a helper class for QCborArray and QCborMap. It is the type you get when using one of the mutating APIs in those classes. Unlike QCborValue, new values can be assigned to that class. When that is done, the array or map it refers to will be modified with the new value. trans-unit.source: QConcatenateTablesProxyModel handles dropping onto an item, between items, and after the last item. In all cases the call is forwarded to the underlying source model. trans-unit.source: QContiguousCache operates on a fixed capacity, set with setCapacity() or passed as a parameter to the constructor. This capacity is the upper bound on memory usage by the cache itself, not including the memory allocated by the elements themselves. Note that a cache with a capacity of zero (the default) means no items will be stored: the insert(), append() and prepend() operations will effectively be no-ops. Therefore, it's important to set the capacity to a reasonable value before adding items to the cache.
trans-unit.target: QContiguousCache以setCapacity（）设置或作为参数传递给构造函数的固定容量运行。此容量是高速缓存本身对内存使用量的上限，不包括元素本身分配的内存。请注意，容量为零（默认）的缓存意味着将不存储任何项目：insert（），append（）和prepend（）操作将实际上是无操作的。因此，在将项目添加到缓存之前，必须将容量设置为合理的值，这一点很重要。

trans-unit.source: QContiguousCache<T> provides an efficient way of caching data that is typically accessed in a contiguous way.
trans-unit.target: QContiguousCache <T>提供了一种缓存数据的有效方法，该数据通常以连续的方式访问。

trans-unit.source: postEvent() is also used during object initialization, since the posted event will typically be dispatched very soon after the initialization of the object is complete. When implementing a widget, it is important to realize that events can be delivered very early in its lifetime so, in its constructor, be sure to initialize member variables early on, before there's any chance that it might receive an event.
trans-unit.target: postEvent（）也用于对象初始化期间，因为通常在对象初始化完成后很快就调度发布的事件。在实现小部件时，重要的是要意识到事件可以在其生命周期的很早就交付，因此，在其构造函数中，一定要在有可能接收事件之前尽早初始化成员变量。

trans-unit.source: postEvent() posts the event on a queue for later dispatch. The next time Qt's main event loop runs, it dispatches all posted events, with some optimization. For example, if there are several resize events, they are compressed into one. The same applies to paint events: QWidget::update() calls postEvent(), which eliminates flickering and increases speed by avoiding multiple repaints.
trans-unit.target: postEvent（）将事件发布到队列中，以供以后分派。下次Qt的主事件循环运行时，它将分派所有已发布的事件，并进行一些优化。例如，如果有多个调整大小事件，它们将被压缩为一个。这同样适用于绘画事件：QWidget :: update（）调用postEvent（），通过避免多次重新绘画来消除闪烁并提高速度。

trans-unit.source: sendEvent() processes the event immediately. When it returns, the event filters and/or the object itself have already processed the event. trans-unit.target: sendEvent（）立即处理事件。返回时，事件过滤器和/或对象本身已经处理了事件。对于许多事件类，有一个名为isAccepted（）的函数，该函数告诉您事件是被最后一个调用的处理程序接受还是拒绝。

trans-unit.source: QDateTime can describe datetimes with respect to local time, to UTC, to a specified offset from UTC or to a specified time zone, in conjunction with the QTimeZone class. For example, a time zone of "Europe/Berlin" will apply the daylight-saving rules as used in Germany since 1970. In contrast, an offset from UTC of +3600 seconds is one hour ahead of UTC (usually written in ISO standard notation as "UTC+01:00"), with no daylight-saving offset or changes. When using either local time or a specified time zone, time-zone transitions such as the starts and ends of daylight-saving time (DST) are taken into account. The choice of system used to represent a datetime is described as its "timespec".
trans-unit.target: QDateTime可以与QTimeZone类一起描述相对于本地时间，UTC，UTC的指定偏移量或指定时区的日期时间。例如，“欧洲/柏林”时区将应用自1970年以来德国使用的夏令时规则。相比之下，与UTC的偏移量为3600秒比UTC早一小时（通常以ISO标准符号表示）如“ UTC + 01：00”），没有夏令时偏移或更改。使用本地时间或指定的时区时，将考虑时区转换，例如夏令时（DST）的开始和结束。用于表示日期时间的系统选择称为“时间规格”。

trans-unit.source: QDateTime likewise uses system-provided information to determine the offsets of other timezones from UTC. If this information is incomplete or out of date, QDateTime will give wrong results. See the QTimeZone documentation for more details.
trans-unit.target: QDateTime同样使用系统提供的信息来确定其他时区与UTC的偏移量。如果此信息不完整或过时，则QDateTime将给出错误的结果。有关更多详细信息，请参见QTimeZone文档。

trans-unit.source: QDateTime provides a full set of operators to compare two QDateTime objects, where smaller means earlier and larger means later.
trans-unit.target: QDateTime提供了一整套运算符来比较两个QDateTime对象，其中较小的表示较早，较大的表示较晚。

trans-unit.source: QDateTime takes into account transitions between Standard Time and Daylight-Saving Time. For example, if the transition is at 2am and the clock goes forward to 3am, then there is a "missing" hour from 02:00:00 to 02:59:59.999 which QDateTime considers to be invalid. Any date arithmetic performed will take this missing hour into account and return a valid result. For example, adding one minute to 01:59:59 will get 03:00:00.
trans-unit.target: QDateTime考虑了标准时间和夏时制之间的转换。例如，如果过渡是在凌晨2点和时钟前进到凌晨3点，再有就是从02:00:00至02一个“失踪”的时间：59：59.999这QDateTime认为是无效的。执行的任何日期算术都将考虑这个缺少的小时并返回有效结果。例如，将一分钟添加到01:59:59将获得03:00:00。

trans-unit.source: QDateTime uses the system's time zone information to determine the current local time zone and its offset from UTC. If the system is not configured correctly or not up-to-date, QDateTime will give wrong results.
trans-unit.target: QDateTime使用系统的时区信息来确定当前本地时区及其与UTC的偏移量。如果系统配置不正确或不是最新的，则QDateTime将给出错误的结果。

trans-unit.source: QDateTime: a date and time stamp

QDateTime::currentDateTime() returns a QDateTime that expresses the current time with respect to local time. QDateTime::currentDateTimeUtc() returns a QDateTime that expresses the current time with respect to UTC.
trans-unit.target: QDateTime :: currentDateTime（）返回一个QDateTime，它表示相对于本地时间的当前时间。QDateTime :: currentDateTimeUtc（）返回一个QDateTime，它表示相对于UTC的当前时间。

trans-unit.source: QDateTime::currentDateTime() returns a QDateTime that expresses the current time with respect to local time. QDateTime::currentDateTimeUtc() returns a QDateTime that expresses the current time with respect to UTC.

QDateTimeAxis can be set up to show an axis line with tick marks, grid lines, and shades. The labels can be configured by setting an appropriate DateTime format. QDateTimeAxis works correctly with dates from 4714 BCE to 287396 CE. For other limitiations related to QDateTime, see QDateTime documentation.
trans-unit.target: 可以将QDateTimeAxis设置为显示带有刻度线，网格线和阴影的轴线。可以通过设置适当的DateTime格式来配置标签。QDateTimeAxis可以正确使用从4714 BCE到287396 CE的日期。对于与其他limitiations QDateTime，见QDateTime文档。

trans-unit.source: QDateTimeEdit (8) provides a widget for editing dates and times.
trans-unit.target: QDateTimeEdit（8）提供了一个用于编辑日期和时间的小部件。

trans-unit.source: QDateTimeEdit allows the user to edit dates by using the keyboard or the arrow keys to increase and decrease date and time values. The arrow keys can be used to move from section to section within the QDateTimeEdit box. Dates and times appear in accordance with the format set; see setDisplayFormat().
trans-unit.target: QDateTimeEdit允许用户使用键盘或箭头键编辑日期，以增加和减少日期和时间值。箭头键可用于在QDateTimeEdit框中的一个区域移动。日期和时间按照设置的格式显示；请参见setDisplayFormat（）。

trans-unit.source: QDateTimeEdit can be configured to allow a QCalendarWidget to be used to select dates. This is enabled by setting the calendarPopup property. Additionally, you can supply a custom calendar widget for use as the calendar pop-up by calling the setCalendarWidget() function. The existing calendar widget can be retrieved with calendarWidget().
trans-unit.target: QDateTimeEdit可以被配置为允许QCalendarWidget被用来选择日期。这可以通过设置calendarPopup属性来启用。此外，您可以通过调用setCalendarWidget（）函数来提供自定义日历小部件，以用作日历弹出窗口。可以使用calendarWidget（）检索现有的日历小部件。

trans-unit.source: date holds the date displayed by the widget.
displayFormat contains a string that is used to format the date displayed in the widget.
trans-unit.target: displayFormat包含一个字符串，用于格式化窗口小部件中显示的日期。

trans-unit.source: displayFormat contains a string that is used to format the time displayed in the widget.
trans-unit.target: displayFormat包含一个字符串，用于格式化窗口小部件中显示的时间。

trans-unit.source: maximumDate defines the maximum (latest) date that can be set by the user.
trans-unit.target: maximumDate定义用户可以设置的最大（最新）日期。

trans-unit.source: maximumTime defines the maximum (latest) time that can be set by the user.
trans-unit.target: maximumTime定义用户可以设置的最大（最新）时间。

trans-unit.source: minimumDate defines the minimum (earliest) date that can be set by the user.
trans-unit.target: minimumDate定义用户可以设置的最短（最早）日期。

trans-unit.source: minimumTime defines the minimum (earliest) time that can be set by the user.
trans-unit.target: minimumTime定义用户可以设置的最短（最早）时间。

trans-unit.source: time holds the time displayed by the widget.
trans-unit.target: 时间保存小部件显示的时间。

trans-unit.source: QDBusAbstractAdaptor uses the standard QObject mechanism of signals, slots and properties to determine what signals, methods and properties to export to the bus. Any signal emitted by QDBusAbstractAdaptor-derived classes will be automatically be relayed through any D-Bus connections the object is registered on.
trans-unit.target: QDBusAbstractAdaptor使用信号，插槽和属性的标准QObject机制来确定要输出到总线的信号，方法和属性。QDBusAbstractAdaptor派生的类发出的任何信号都将通过对象注册到的任何D-Bus连接自动中继。

trans-unit.source: QDBusArgument is the central class in the Qt D-Bus type system, providing functions to marshall and demarshall the primitive types. The compound types are then created by association of one or more of the primitive types in arrays, dictionaries or structures.
trans-unit.target: QDBusArgument是Qt D-Bus类型系统的中心类，提供封送和解组原始类型的功能。然后通过将数组，字典或结构中的一种或多种原始类型关联起来来创建复合类型。

trans-unit.source: QDBusError contains an error that is not one of the well-known ones
trans-unit.target: QDBusError包含不是众所周知的错误之一的错误

trans-unit.source: QDBusError is invalid (i.e., the call succeeded)

QDBusError objects are used to inspect the error name and message as received from the bus and remote applications. You should not create such objects yourself to signal error conditions when called from D-Bus: instead, use QDBusMessage::createError() and QDBusConnection::send().
trans-unit.target: QDBusError对象用于检查从总线和远程应用程序收到的错误名称和消息。从D-Bus调用时，您不应该自己创建此类对象来发出错误情况信号：相反，请使用QDBusMessage :: createError（）和QDBusConnection :: send（）。

trans-unit.source: QDBusInterface is a generic accessor class that is used to place calls to remote objects, connect to signals exported by remote objects and get/set the value of remote properties. This class is useful for dynamic access to remote objects: that is, when you do not have a generated code that represents the remote interface.
trans-unit.target: QDBusInterface是一个通用的访问器类，用于对远程对象进行调用，连接到远程对象导出的信号以及获取/设置远程属性的值。此类对于动态访问远程对象很有用：也就是说，当您没有代表远程接口的生成代码时。

trans-unit.source: QDBusPendingReply object. Just like QDBusPendingCall and QDBusPendingCallWatcher, this QDBusPendingReply object will share the same pending call reference. All copies share the same return values.
trans-unit.target: QDBusPendingReply对象。就像QDBusPendingCall和QDBusPendingCallWatcher一样，此QDBusPendingReply对象将共享相同的未决调用引用。所有副本都具有相同的返回值。

trans-unit.source: QDBusPendingReply objects can be associated with QDBusPendingCallWatcher objects, which emit signals when the reply arrives.
trans-unit.target: QDBusPendingReply对象可以与QDBusPendingCallWatcher对象相关联，该对象在答复到达时发出信号。

trans-unit.source: QDBusPendingReply<T1, T2, T3, T4, T5, T6, T7, T8> &QDBusPendingReply::operator=(const QDBusMessage &
QDBusPendingReply<T1, T2, T3, T4, T5, T6, T7, T8> &QDBusPendingReply::operator=(const QDBusPendingCall &

QDBusReply accepts exactly one return type, whereas QDBusPendingReply can have from 1 to 8 types
trans-unit.target: QDBusReply只能接受一种返回类型，而QDBusPendingReply可以具有1到8种类型

trans-unit.source: QDBusReply accepts exactly one return type, whereas QDBusPendingReply can have from 1 to 8 types
QDBusReply objects are used for remote calls that have no output arguments or return values (i.e., they have a "void" return type). Use the isValid() function to test if the reply succeeded.
trans-unit.target: QDBusReply对象用于没有输出参数或返回值的远程调用（即，它们具有“ void”返回类型）。使用isValid（）函数测试回复是否成功。

trans-unit.source: QDBusReply only works on already completed replies, whereas QDBusPendingReply allows one to wait for replies from pending calls
trans-unit.target: QDBusReply仅适用于已经完成的答复，而QDBusPendingReply允许等待来自未决呼叫的答复

trans-unit.source: QDBusReply only works on already completed replies, whereas QDBusPendingReply allows one to wait for replies from pending calls

trans-unit.source: QDBusUnixFileDescriptor does not take ownership of the file descriptor. Instead, it will use the Unix system call dup(2) to make a copy of the file descriptor. This file descriptor belongs to the QDBusUnixFileDescriptor object and should not be stored or closed by the user. Instead, you should make your own copy if you need that.
trans-unit.target: QDBusUnixFileDescriptor不拥有文件描述符的所有权。相反，它将使用Unix系统调用 dup(2) 来制作文件描述符的副本。该文件描述符属于QDBusUnixFileDescriptor对象，并且不应由用户存储或关闭。相反，如果需要，您应该制作自己的副本。

trans-unit.source: QDBusUnixFileDescriptor object. If the current object contained a file descriptor, it will be properly disposed of before.
trans-unit.target: QDBusUnixFileDescriptor对象。如果当前对象包含文件描述符，则将其正确处置。

trans-unit.source: QDeadlineTimer defaults to Qt::CoarseTimer because on operating systems that do support coarse timing, making timing calls to that clock source is often much more efficient. The level of coarseness depends on the operating system, but should be in the order of a couple of milliseconds.
trans-unit.target: QDeadlineTimer默认为Qt :: CoarseTimer，因为在支持粗略计时的操作系统上，对该时钟源进行计时调用通常会更加高效。粗糙程度取决于操作系统，但应在几毫秒的数量级上。

trans-unit.source: QDeadlineTimer objects created with ForeverConstant never expire. For such objects, remainingTime() will return -1, deadline() will return the maximum value, and isForever() will return true.
trans-unit.target: QDeadlineTimer对象与创建ForeverConstant永不过期。对于此类对象，剩余时间（）将返回-1，截止日期（）将返回最大值，而isForever（）将返回true。

trans-unit.source: QDeadlineTimer objects created with the ForeverConstant never expire and this function always returns false for them.
trans-unit.target: QDeadlineTimer对象与创建ForeverConstant永不过期而这个函数总是返回false他们。

trans-unit.source: QDeadlineTimer provides a more convenient API compared to QElapsedTimer::hasExpired().
trans-unit.target: 与QElapsedTimer :: hasExpired（）相比，QDeadlineTimer提供了更方便的API 。

trans-unit.source: QDeadlineTimer will use the same clock as QElapsedTimer (see QElapsedTimer::clockType() and QElapsedTimer::isMonotonic()).
trans-unit.target: QDeadlineTimer将使用与QElapsedTimer相同的时钟（请参阅QElapsedTimer :: clockType（）和QElapsedTimer :: isMonotonic（））。
